        <p>West Hollywood is Los Angeles' entertainment capital, known for its vibrant nightlife, trendy bars, and world-class dining scene. With 17 exceptional date night restaurants, this neighborhood offers everything from intimate rooftop dining to cozy neighborhood bistros perfect for romantic evenings.</p>
        
