          <div class="highlight-card">
            <h3>üé≠ Entertainment District</h3>
            <p>Located in the heart of LA's entertainment industry, West Hollywood offers a glamorous backdrop for romantic dinners with easy access to theaters, clubs, and cultural venues.</p>
          </div>
          
