            <h3>üåÜ Rooftop Dining</h3>
            <p>Many restaurants feature stunning rooftop patios with panoramic views of the Hollywood Hills and downtown LA skyline, creating unforgettable romantic settings.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <h3>üç∑ Wine & Cocktail Scene</h3>
            <p>West Hollywood is home to some of LA's best wine bars and craft cocktail lounges, perfect for pre-dinner drinks or post-dinner nightcaps.</p>
          </div>
          
