            <h3>üö∂ Walkable Streets</h3>
            <p>The neighborhood's pedestrian-friendly streets make it easy to stroll between restaurants, bars, and entertainment venues for a complete evening out.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Cuisine Diversity -->
      <section class="cuisine-diversity">
        <h2>Diverse Culinary Experiences</h2>
        <p>West Hollywood's restaurant scene reflects LA's multicultural dining landscape, offering couples the opportunity to explore cuisines from around the world:</p>
        
        <ul class="cuisine-list">
          {cuisineTypes.slice(0, 8).map(cuisine => (
            <li><a href={`/cuisines/${cuisine.toLowerCase().replace(/\s+/g, '-')}/`}>{cuisine}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        
        <p>From authentic Italian trattorias to modern fusion concepts, each restaurant brings its own unique atmosphere and culinary expertise to create memorable date night experiences.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Planning Your Date Night -->
      <section class="planning-tips">
        <h2>Planning Your West Hollywood Date Night</h2>
        
        <div class="tips-grid">
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üïê Best Times to Visit</h3>
            <p>Weekday evenings (Tuesday-Thursday) offer a more intimate atmosphere with easier reservations. Weekend nights are livelier but require advance booking.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üÖøÔ∏è Parking Tips</h3>
            <p>Street parking can be challenging. Consider valet parking at restaurants or use ride-sharing services for a stress-free evening.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üëó Dress Code</h3>
            <p>West Hollywood restaurants range from casual to upscale. Check restaurant websites for specific dress codes, but smart casual is generally appropriate.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üìÖ Reservations</h3>
            <p>Popular restaurants book up quickly, especially on weekends. Make reservations 1-2 weeks in advance for the best selection.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Related Content -->
      <section class="related-content">
        <h2>Explore More Date Night Options</h2>
        <div class="related-links">
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/west-hollywood/" class="related-link">
            <h3>All West Hollywood Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Browse our complete list of {westHollywoodRestaurants.length} restaurants in West Hollywood</p>
          </a>
          
