            <h3>Santa Monica Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Discover romantic oceanfront dining in Santa Monica</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/downtown-la/" class="related-link">
            <h3>Downtown LA Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Explore urban dining experiences in downtown Los Angeles</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/blog/best-rooftop-restaurants-los-angeles-date-night/" class="related-link">
            <h3>Best Rooftop Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Find the perfect rooftop dining spots for romantic evenings</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>Ready for Your Next Date Night?</h2>
        <p>With 17 exceptional restaurants to choose from, West Hollywood offers endless possibilities for romantic dining. Whether you're planning a special celebration or a casual date night, you're sure to find the perfect spot.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/west-hollywood/" class="btn btn-primary">View All West Hollywood Restaurants</a>
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore All LA Restaurants</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

